================================================================================
Session: Custom AMI for AWS Batch workers — 2026-04-26
Branch: I14-custom-ami-worker
================================================================================

## Session goal

Eliminate the 20+ minute S3 sync at worker boot by building a custom AMI with
databases pre-baked. This is the implementation of I14 (issues/I14-custom-ami-worker.md),
which supersedes ADR-001's S3-sync approach.

## Prior sessions (same day)

  1. infra-debug-guardrails — diagnosed ChocoPhlAn DB missing (ECS race condition),
     deployed stop-ecs fix, added agents/skills/guardrails.
  2. launch-template-propagation-fix — discovered Batch doesn't auto-propagate
     LT changes, forced CE update, ran smoke tests #6-#7 (both failed: #6 had
     stale LT, #7 timed out during 20-min S3 sync). Decision: custom AMI.

