2. BATCH-STACK.YAML CHANGES — STAGED (NOT YET DEPLOYED)
================================================================================

  Modified infra/batch-stack.yaml (uncommitted on I14-custom-ami-worker branch):

  a) EcsAmiId parameter description: updated to reference custom AMI and SSM
     lookup instead of stock AL2023 AMI lookup command.

  b) DbSourceBucket parameter description: clarified that it's now used only
     for IAM policy permissions, not for boot-time sync.

  c) Launch template comments: simplified to reflect pre-baked AMI approach.

